# Episodes to Highlight (Good vs Bad Performance)

These shaded windows act like “chapters” in the story.

```{r episodes}
episodes <- tibble::tribble(
  ~label, ~start, ~end,
  "Dot-com / 9-11 easing", as.Date("2001-01-01"), as.Date("2003-12-01"),
  "GFC: cuts + unemployment spike", as.Date("2007-12-01"), as.Date("2010-12-01"),
  "Long expansion (low U, low-ish infl)", as.Date("2015-12-01"), as.Date("2019-12-01"),
  "Pandemic shock", as.Date("2020-03-01"), as.Date("2021-06-01"),
  "Inflation surge + fastest hikes", as.Date("2021-07-01"), end_date
)

shade <- function(p) {
  p + geom_rect(
    data = episodes,
    aes(xmin = start, xmax = end, ymin = -Inf, ymax = Inf),
    inherit.aes = FALSE,
    alpha = 0.08
  )
}
```

